@*
    =====================================================================
    File: Pages/Shared/_ValidationScriptsPartial.cshtml

    Purpose:
        Reusable partial view that emits the <script> tags for jQuery
        Validation and its unobtrusive adapter. Include it on any form
        page that uses [DataAnnotations]-driven client-side validation:

            @section Scripts {
                <partial name="_ValidationScriptsPartial" />
            }

    Notes:
        * The script paths point at the default wwwroot/lib/ locations
          created by the Razor Pages project template.
        * This file is currently unused by the Heather UI (the chat
          forms don't rely on data-annotation validation), but is kept
          to match the standard template and to be available if needed.
    =====================================================================
*@
<script src="~/lib/jquery-validation/dist/jquery.validate.min.js"></script>
<script src="~/lib/jquery-validation-unobtrusive/dist/jquery.validate.unobtrusive.min.js"></script>
